<HEADLINE>
FT  11 NOV 94 / World News in Brief: Polish minister sacked
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Polish president Lech Walesa sacked defence minister Piotr Kolodziejczyk,
his erstwhile ally, following a bitter row over reforms in the armed forces.
</TEXT>
